(52, 1, '2016-02-25 00:57:04', '2016-02-25 00:57:04', 'Symmetry guarantees satisfaction with its services or will refund client membership fees in full within the first 30-days of the membership. A refund under the Guarantee must be claimed in writing by Day-30 of the membership; no specific reason need be provided. The client will otherwise be deemed happy to continue for the remaining membership period..', 'Guarantee', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'guarantee', '', '', '2016-02-25 00:57:25', '2016-02-25 00:57:25', '', 0, 'http://care.gsqtest1.com/?page_id=52', 0, 'page', '', 0),
